# Challenge Description:
Link: http://find-pass-code-one.kshackzone.com/
Hint: Hi Serafin, I learned something new today. 
I build this website for you to verify our KnightCTF 2022 pass code. You can view the source code by sending the source param.

#Solution:
+ Find we check for the source param:  http://find-pass-code-one.kshackzone.com/?source
+ There we can see the php code of the page
+ We can solve the challenge using loose comparison vulnerability
+ We will open the page in burp and change it to GET to POST
+ In the response body, we will give "pass_code[]=0"


